nning right now.\"}]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "Implemented the follow-up coverage refinement for `net.sf.cglib.asm.ClassReader`.\n\nChanges made:\n- Added dedicated active-class test:\n  - `tests/src/cglib/cglib-nodep/2.2.2/src/test/java/cglib/cglib_nodep/ClassReaderTest.java`\n  - Exercises `new ClassReader(ClassReader.class.getName())`, which invokes `ClassLoader#getSystemResourceAsStream(String)` from the `ClassReader(String)` constructor.\n- Added Native Image resource metadata:\n  - `metadata/cglib/cglib-nodep/2.2.2/reachability-metadata.json`\n- Updated dynamic-access coverage reporting support:\n  - `tests/tck-build-logic/src/main/java/org/graalvm/internal/tck/stats/LibraryStatsSupport.java`\n  - The active call site is reported as `Unknown Source`, so line-based JaCoCo matching cannot mark it covered. I added a method-coverage fallback for dynamic-access frames without line numbers, so line-less library bytecode can still be credited when JaCoCo shows the containing method executed.\n\nPer instruction, I did not compile or run tests locally.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_02b7b9ea67e49d9a0169f5aab5f7b88191be9f0996e2ca560b\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 453, "output": 1269, "cacheRead": 59904, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 61626, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777707684738, "responseId": "resp_02b7b9ea67e49d9a0169f5aaa5576c819196e6aee2fc7e79c5"}}
